{"tid":473591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★窮人報告：本港最多貧窮人口---1 居屋 2公屋 3 私樓......","createTime":"2017-11-19T11:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T03:36:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb0e80d39cf475f186221d509ff38358ed9ae07","tid":473591,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最多窮人住自置居所</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，報告揭示政策介入後，<span style=\"color: red;\">最多貧窮人口住在自置居所，即居屋約四十五萬七千人，貧窮率達四成五</span>。報告估計，因住在自置居所的多為沒有從事經濟活動及長者，亦有部分屬「低收入，高資產」退休長者，貧窮率因而較高。公屋及私樓貧窮率雖未如自置居所高企，但兩組有兒童住戶的貧窮率分別為三成八及五成六，遠高於整體貧窮住戶的兩成七，反映家庭負擔重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171119/00176_040.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171119%2F00176_040.html&d=HNVg101uNyMcsaW4z%2FgQbozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=dc042cd2\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171119/00176_040.html</a>"},{"pid":"1e2ca54e93f94811527942d375185d19374eecd9","tid":473591,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"公屋 win<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844766e596a09ddfe9738f7aeee02a643f592716","tid":473591,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:34:43.000Z","msg":"供完居屋變窮撚，不如及早食老綜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0358693b1abd7d7fbdb1d4dd3b8259866f9532bd","tid":473591,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:36:01.000Z","msg":"45%窮撚身在居屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da816f41e969c93ae719c2572f2b85cfc2be04e","tid":473591,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:38:43.000Z